overlay-root (3.0.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Modified 2023 by m4dm4x1337 (fixed 2 bugs, see v3.0.0 changelog)
    - Resolve root fs symlink if any (e.g. /dev/mapper/ link if root
      is encrypted)
    - Taking tabs into account in /etc/fstab

 -- m4dm4x1337 <madmax@earth.local>  Sun, 29 Oct 2023 01:00:00 +0000

overlay-root (2.0.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Modified 2015 by Pascal Rosin to work on raspian-ua-netinst with overlayfs
    integrated in Linux Kernel >= 3.18.
    - Modified to work with overlayfs integrated in Linux Kernel (>= 3.18)
    - Introduced workdir needed for new overlayfs
    - Changed `mount --move` to `mount -o move` to drop busybox requirement
    - Tested with raspian-ua-netinst v1.0.7 (Linux 3.18.0-trunk-rpi,
      Debian 3.18.5) on a Raspberry Pi. The aufs part is not tested!

 -- m4dm4x1337 <madmax@earth.local>  Sun, 29 Oct 2023 00:30:00 +0000

